<\body>
  <tmdoc-title|Internationalization of <TeXmacs>>

  <\description>
    <item*|Chinese>Chu-Ching Huang and Zou-Hu.

    <item*|Croatian>Luka Marohni.

    <item*|Czech>David Rezac.

    <item*|Danish>Magnus Marius Rohde.

