    <item*|French>Michle Garoche, Joris van der Hoeven.

    <item*|German>Dietmar Jung, Hans Dembinski, Jan Ulrich Hasecke, Christoph
    Strobel, Joris van der Hoeven, Thomas Langen, Ralf Treinen.

    <item*|Greek>Alkis Akritas.

    <item*|Hungarian>Andrs Kadinger.

    <item*|Italian>Andrea Centomo, Lucia Gecchelin, Xav and Daniele Pighin,
    Gian Luigi Gragnani.

    <item*|Japanese>Nobuki Takayama.

    <item*|Korean>Karnes Kim.

    <item*|Polish>Robert Janusz, Emil Nowak, Jan Alboszta.

    <item*|Portuguese>Ramiro Brito Willmersdorf, Mrcio Laurini, Alexandre
    Taschetto de Castro.

    <item*|Romanian>Dan Ignat.

    <item*|Russian>Andrey Grozin.

    <item*|Slovene>Ziga Kranjec.

    <item*|Spanish>lvaro Cantero Tejero, Pablo Ruiz Mzquiz, David Moriano
    Garcia, Offray Vladimir Luna Crdenas.

    <item*|Swedish>Harald Ellmann.

    <item*|Taiwanese>Chu-Ching Huang.

    <item*|Ukrainian>Volodymyr Lisivka.
  </description>

